D225 state road shield State roads in Croatia D225 is a state road in the central Croatia connecting Harmica border crossing to Slovenia and the city of Zaprei to the A2 motorway in Zaprei interchange.[1] The road is 14.8km (9.2mi) long.[2] The road, as well as all other state roads in Croatia, is managed and maintained by Hrvatske ceste, state owned company.[3] Traffic is regularly counted and reported by Hrvatske ceste, operator of the road.[4]
